### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### --- Tickets ---

### Create a ticket
# POST http://localhost:8080/tickets
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "title": "Login page returns 500",
#   "description": "Users see an internal server error on the login page.",
#   "priority": "P1",
#   "assignee": "alice"
# }

### List tickets
# GET http://localhost:8080/tickets?status=OPEN&priority=P1

### Get a ticket by ID
# GET http://localhost:8080/tickets/1

### Update a ticket
# PATCH http://localhost:8080/tickets/1
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
# }

### --- Comments ---

### Add a comment
# POST http://localhost:8080/tickets/1/comments
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "author": "bob",
#   "body": "Looking into this now."
# }

### --- Events ---

### Get ticket events
# GET http://localhost:8080/tickets/1/events
